for the month before last.

57
00:04:21,840 --> 00:04:23,432
OK.

58
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:26,279
I guess I'll be hitting the road.

59
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:33,357
Joel... why am I on the schedule?

60
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:35,550
Sorry, wishful thinking.

61
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:38,956
